# Petri 3.0 Open-Source Alignment Tool

**Title:** Donating our open-source alignment tool

**Full URL:** https://www.anthropic.com/research/donating-open-source-petri

**Publication Date:** 2026-05-07

**Authors:** Not specified in the article

**Summary:**

Anthropic has transferred Petri, an open-source evaluation framework, to Meridian Labs to ensure its independence and credibility across the AI industry. The tool "can be used to rapidly and easily test AI models for concerning tendencies like deception, sycophancy, and cooperation with harmful requests," making it valuable for alignment researchers evaluating model behavior. Version 3.0 introduces enhanced adaptability, improved realism through the "Dish" add-on, and deeper assessment capabilities by integrating with the Bloom tool, strengthening the broader ecosystem of neutral AI evaluation technologies.

